sequenceDiagram
    participant System
    participant Server
    participant DB
    participant SMTP
    participant Twilio

    System->>Server: add_notification(recipient, ...)
    Server->>DB: create Notification (in-app)
    DB-->>Server: saved notification
    alt recipient.email
        Server->>SMTP: send_mail(subject, message)
        SMTP-->>Server: success/failure
    end
    alt recipient.phone
        opt Twilio configured
            Server->>Twilio: client.messages.create(...)
            Twilio-->>Server: success/failure
        else
            Server-->>Server: log SMS (mock)
        end
    end
